=== The Gradient ===
--- gradient: pure function ---
double: (Int) -> Int
  -> double is Pure
     add 'with Pure' to unlock:
       memoization  (same input = same output, guaranteed)
       parallelism  (no side effects to race)
       compile-time (if inputs are known, evaluate at build)

--- gradient: effectful function ---
reader: () -> ?2 with IO
  -> reader does not access network
     add 'with !Network' to prove:
       sandboxed  (capability restriction as types)

--- gradient: already annotated ---
safe: (Int) -> Int

